headline: Procter & Gamble Delivers, But Is Volume Growth Still a Worry?
summary: PG posts solid Q1 earnings via pricing and productivity, but weak volume in North America raises doubts about sustaining top-line momentum.

headline: Church & Dwight to Webcast the 2026 Analyst Day and Full Year 2025 Earnings Results on January 30
summary: EWING, N.J., January 05, 2026--Church & Dwight Co., Inc. (NYSE: CHD) will host a webcast from the Church & Dwight 2026 Analyst Day to discuss fourth quarter and year end 2025 earnings results on January 30, 2026, at 12:00 p.m. ET.
